t:
After pushing for an hour,
my child's head finally started to crown.



My happiness was short-lived when only the head came out.
c:
Everyone was horrified when the head spoke.

crown
/kra än/
(of a baby's head during labour) fully appear in the vaginal opening prior to emerging.
